'''Adare Trough''' is an undersea [[trough (geology)|trough]] name proposed by Dr. [[Steven C. Cande]], [[Scripps Institution of Oceanography]]. Named in association with [[Adare Peninsula]] and [[Cape Adare]]. Name approved by the [[Advisory Committee on Undersea Features]] in September 1997.

