{{Politics of Saint Pierre and Miquelon}}
This article lists '''political parties in Saint Pierre and Miquelon'''. [[Saint Pierre and Miquelon]] has a [[multi-party system]], in which some of the [[List of political parties in France|French political parties]] are active. They participate in the elections through either Saint Pierre or Miquelon lists. At the last elections the following lists took part: *Saint Pierre and Miquelon 2000 (Saint Pierre et Miquelon 2000, related to the [[Socialist Party (France)|Socialist Party]]) *Future Miquelon (Miquelon Avenir, related to the [[Socialist Party (France)|Socialist Party]]) *Road to the Future (Cap sur l'Avenir, related to the [[Radical Party of the Left]]) *[[Archipelago Tomorrow]] (Archipel Demain, related to the [[Union for a Popular Movement]]) *Miquelon Objectives (Objectifs Miquelonnais, related to the [[Union for a Popular Movement]])
==See also== * [[Politics of Saint Pierre and Miquelon]] * [[List of political parties by country]]
