[[Image:Samakhusi.jpg|Samakhushi|250px|right]]

'''Samakhushi''' is an urban city in [[Nepal]] located within [[Kathmandu]]. It is roughly 10 minutes from Golkopakha, [[Thamel]]. Samakhushi has various guesthouses and offers a vibrant ethnic cultural taste.

Samakhushi is one of the cities within Kathmandu which is viewed as a peaceful area.

Samakhusi is approximately 15 minutes drive from Bus Park from where there are services to major towns and cities in Nepal.

