==Calling formats== * '''xxx xxxx''' - calls within an area code * '''0yy xxx xxxx''' - calling within [[Ethiopia]] * '''+251 yy xxx xxxx''' Calling from outside Ethiopia The NSN length is nine digits.
Mobile numbers start with 91
'''091 XXX-XXXX''' domestic calling
'''+251 91 XXX-XXXX''' from overseas.
